import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Spinner } from '../src'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"spinner"}}>{`Spinner`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"default"}}>{`Default`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Spinner />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"small"}}>{`Small`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Spinner size="small" />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner size='small' />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"medium"}}>{`Medium`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Spinner size="medium" />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner size='medium' />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"large"}}>{`Large`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Spinner size="large" />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner size='large' />
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"custom-size"}}>{`Custom size`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Spinner width={10} height={50} />`} __scope={{props,Spinner}}>
  <Spinner width={10} height={50} />
</Playground></MDXTag>
